claim: Joseph Fiennes has worked in tv acting.
premise_source_doc_sentence: He is known for his portrayals of William Shakespeare in Shakespeare in Love  (  1998  )  , for which he was nominated for the BAFTA Award for Best Actor in a Leading Role and the Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Male Actor in a Leading Role , Sir Robert Dudley in Elizabeth  (  1998  )  , Commisar Danilov in Enemy at the Gates  (  2001  )  , and Monsignor Timothy Howard in the second season of the TV series American Horror Story  (  2012 -- 2013  )  .
